snippet.title: Alien Disco Safari (Windows game 2007)
snippet.description:
Alien Disco Safari is a 3D graphics light gun shooter game developed by L39 Studios.
You must shoot at many aliens to obtain more than aim points (scores).
If you get fewer than aim points, you will not enter the next mission.
